{
  "stem": "25598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Other people heard that it's better more in the interior.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there were rumors for this, rumors for that, and nobody knew what the reality is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So-- so obviously, my parents were those who believed that it's better in the interior.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we joined this convoy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The march was a horrific experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "First of all, we slept in the fields and ditches in the rain, surrounded by the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Secondly, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Most importantly, and most traumatically, whoever couldn't keep up with the march remained behind and was shot by the soldiers or were simply left in the mud.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- and peasants came and took their clothes off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And eventually they died or were eaten by wild animals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And of course, the people who couldn't walk were mostly elderly people, the grandparents, and the-- and children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As much as the parents wanted to carry them, in families where there were more than two children, they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So a lot of people perished on-- on this march.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when we got to-- to Mogilev, we were-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --we were allowed to find lodging by ourselves with some of the local Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we paid for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we went-- we lived with a-- in a hut-- very primitive hut-- no toilet, no running water, no furniture, earth floors, just a stove.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was some kind of a primitive stove in which they were baking bread and cooking at the same time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was made-- the whole hut was made out of dry manure, and then it was painted on top of that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And-- so it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shargorod.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
